{"word":"ἄπονος","slug":"ἄπονος","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ἄπονος</b></el> <p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><i>without toil</i> or <i>trouble, untroubled, quiet</i>, <b><a href='S:Aeschylus'>Aesch.</a></b>, <a href='S:et cetera'>etc.</a><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b>of persons, <i>not toiling, lazy</i>, <b><a href='S:Xenophon'>Xen.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b><a href='S:Adverb'>adv.</a> <el>-νως</el>, <i>without trouble</i>, <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Xenophon'>Xen.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>III. </b><a href='S:irregular'>irreg.</a> <a href='S:Comparative'>comp.</a> <el>ἀπονέστερος</el>, <b><a href='S:Pindar'>Pind.</a></b>, but <el>-ώτερος</el>, <b><a href='S:Thucydides'>Thuc.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}